SARS-CoV-2 using spike glycoprotein and nucleocapsid antigens.

Javadi Mamaghani A(1), Arab-Mazar Z(2), Heidarzadeh S(3), Ranjbar MM(4), 
Molazadeh S(5), Rashidi S(6), Niazpour F(7), Naghi Vishteh M(1), Bashiri H(8), 
