[Adjusting medication at the end of life: towards optimalisation of healthcare 
in the final fase of life].

[Article in Dutch]

Geijteman ECT(1)(2), Elsten EECM(1), van der Kuy PHMH(3), van der Heide A(4), 
van der Rijt CKCD(1), van Zuylen L(5).

Author information:
(1)Erasmus MC, Rotterdam: Erasmus MC Kanker Instituut, afd. Interne Oncologie.
(2)Contact: Eric C.T. Geijteman (e.geijteman@erasmusmc.nl)).
